 that part of the bargain lando protested hotly you said the interfere in 
 altering the bargain pray i alter it any further 
 a sudden tightness grasped throat a threatening sign of what wouldhappen to him if he gave vader any difficulty hand automatically went tohis neck but in the next moment the unseen hold was released and the administratorturned to face leia and chewbacca the look in his eyes might have expresseddespair but neither of them cared to look at him at all 
 luke and artoo moved cautiously through a deserted corridor 
 it concerned luke that thus far they had not been stopped for questioning noone had asked them for landing permits identification papers purpose of visit noone in cloud city seemed at all curious about who this young man and his little droidmight what they were doing there it all seemed rather ominous and lukewas beginning to feel very uneasy 
